NEWS for cpaa

* version 0.1 (2006-02-02)

- added option "-e" to specify "hook" script.
  following environment variables will be set in execution of the script:
    pana_reason ... "phase" indicates a change of the session phase.
    pana_phase ... the current session phase.
    pana_session_id ... session ID.
    pana_pac_ip_address ... dotted IP address of PaC.

* version 0.1 (2006-01-30)

- added command line option "-d" and "-q" to control verbosity of messages.
- introduced a simple user database feature into cpaa.
  command line option "-u" was also added.
